title: Taylor Tomlinson: A Joke about Mental Health
description: Taylor Tomlinson jokes about mental health in her Netflix special, "Look At You". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Taylor and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
